  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel your <strong>brown onion[s] </strong>and chop in half</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p><p>Add the <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>garlic </strong>and <strong>halved</strong> <strong>onion</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz until finely chopped – this is your <strong>onion & garlic paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606305351911-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606305351911-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606305351911-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606305351911-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1606305351911-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> onion & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground paprika</strong>,<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix and cook for 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606305356710-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606305356710-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606305356710-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606305356710-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1606305356710-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, deseed your <strong>peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop them into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop your <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606305361999-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606305361999-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606305361999-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606305361999-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1606305361999-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> halved</strong> <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong>,<strong> chopped peppers </strong>and <strong>spinach</strong> to the pan with a splash of<strong> cold water</strong>, mix everything together and cook for 1-2 min or until the spinach has wilted</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1606305367467-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1606305367467-x400.jpg",
